降低系统的暂态稳定性为前提则给定的暂态稳定裕度希望取为调整前的稳定裕度值,即<italic>η<sub>set</sub></italic>=<italic>η</italic><sub>0</sub>,若以保证系统不失稳的前提求取断面的极限功率时,则给定的暂态稳定裕度希望取为临界稳定边界对应的稳定裕度<italic>η<sub>cr</sub></italic>,即<italic>η<sub>set</sub></italic>=<italic>η<sub>cr</sub></italic>。</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">需要补充的是,暂态稳定裕度与机组的出力并非严格的线性关系,但利用局部线性化的思想,在基础运行点附近,当机组的出力变化范围较小时,暂态稳定裕度灵敏度可以视为常数,以此指导当前运行方式下的机组出力的调整。若系统的运行方式发生较大变化时,暂态稳定裕度灵敏度需要重新计算。因此,为了保证暂态稳定裕度灵敏度在调整过程中的适用性,有必要对一次调整中机组的出力变化范围加以限制,本文采用机组出力变化范围在当前出力的10%以内为相应的约束：</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-23-Frame\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"display: inline; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px; position: relative;\"><nobr aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"transition: none; border: 0px; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-723\" role=\"math\" style=\"transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; width: 6.574em;\"><span style=\"transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; width: 5.26em; height: 0px; font-size: 17.5px;\"><span style=\"transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; clip: rect(1.489em, 1005.2em, 2.803em, -999.997em); top: -2.397em; left: 0.003em;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-724\" style=\"transition: none; di