>11</a>,<a href=\"http://e-press.dwjs.com.cn/pcsee/periodical/html/2018-38-09-2531.html#b14--0-0-0-1805101434-1\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\">14</a>]</sup>。针对某一基态运行点,断面功率的调整步骤如下：</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">1）计算基态运行方式,确定研究断面和关联故障;</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">2）根据直流潮流模型计算断面功率对系统内机组有功出力的灵敏度<span style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-24-Frame\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"display: inline; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px; position: relative;\"><nobr aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"transition: none; border: 0px; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-741\" role=\"math\" style=\"transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; width: 1.603em;\"><span style=\"transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; width: 1.26em; height: 0px; font-size: 17.5px;\"><span style=\"transition: none; position: absolute; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; clip: rect(1.431em, 1001.26em, 2.86em, -999.997em); top: -2.397em; left: 0.003em;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-742\" style=\"transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-743\" style=\"transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-heigh