ormal; top: -3.883em; left: 0.46em;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-766\" style=\"transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-767\" style=\"transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-768\" style=\"transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;\">G</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-769\" style=\"transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;\">i</span></span></span><span style=\"transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; width: 0px; height: 4.003em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; width: 0px; height: 4.003em;\"></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; width: 0px; height: 2.403em;\"></span></span></span><span style=\"transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border-width: 0px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: solid; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; vertical-align: -0.639em; line-height: normal; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 1.718em;\"></span></span></nobr><span role=\"presentation\" style=\"top: 0px; left: 0px; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); user-select: none; position: static; border: 0px; display: inline; transition: none; vertical-align: 0px; line-height: normal; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important; overflow: hidden !important;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msubsup><mi>s</mi><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>i</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>η</mi></mrow></msubsup></math></span></span>;</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">5）根据给定的机组出力约束、暂态稳定约束等由式(8)—(12)建立断面功率的线性规划模型,从而求得各台机组的有功调整量Δ<italic>P<sub>Gi</sub></italic>;</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">6）针对调整后的发电组合方式,采用暂态稳定性快速评估校核其稳定程度,若当前潮流方式下的暂态稳定裕度<italic>η<sub>new</sub></italic>与给定的希望值<italic>η<sub>set</sub></italic>接近,即满足|<italic>η<sub>new</sub></italic>-<italic>η<sub>set</sub></italic>/<italic>η<sub>set</sub></italic>|≤<italic>ε</italic>,一般取为5%,或当前潮流方式下的暂态稳定裕度小于设定的稳定裕度门槛值<italic>η<sub>thr</sub></italic>,即满足0<<italic>η<sub>new</sub></italic><<italic>η<sub>thr</sub></italic>,则调整结束,输出调整后的断面功率与发电机有功出力;否则返回步骤4。</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\"><xref ref-type=\"fig\" rid=\"F4--0-0-0-1805101434-1\">图4给出了断面功率的调整流程。</xref></p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">由上述断面功率的调整流程可知,通过灵敏度分析的方法,使得在优化机组出力的过程中避免引入潮流方程及动态方程,求解难度大大降低。而且对于一个基态潮流方式总是能够给出机组出力的调整方案,不会存在难以收敛的问题,基于当前潮流方式对机组出力进行调整以提升断面的输送功率在实际中也更具可行性。</p><h4 id=\"outline_anchor_13\" style=\"padding-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; border: none; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; display: inline-block; height: 2rem; width: 0.5rem; background: rgb(118, 212, 118); vertical-align: middle;\"></span> 4 算例分析</h4><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">采用IEEE39节点10机系统验证本文所提断面功率调整方法的可行性。系统共有10台发电机,根据网络拓扑及标准潮流方式下的功率流向,分为3个区域,其中区域A和区域B各有4台发电机,区域C有2台发电机,如<xref ref-type=\"fig\" rid=\"F5--0-0-0-1805101434-1\">图5所示。</xref></p><p state=\"2\" alt=\"图4\" id=\"outline_anchor_14\" style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\"><sapn style=\"width: 150px; clear: right; float: right; margin-top: 1.2rem; margin-left: 1rem; padding-top: 1.2rem; padding-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; border-left: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);\"><a href=\"http://e-press.dwjs.com.cn/pcsee/periodical/html/2018-38-09-2531/img_6.png\" title=\"图4  \r\n            计及暂态稳定约束的断面功率调整流程\r\n           <span>Fig. 4  \r\n            Flow chart of transient stability constrained section active power flow adjustment\r\n          </span>\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\"><img src=\"http://e-press.dwjs.com.cn/pcsee/periodical/html/2018-38-09-2531/img_6.png\" style=\"width: 130px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 1px; display: block;\"></a><span style=\"padding-top: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; border: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.875em; display: block; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.8rem;\">图4 计及暂态稳定约束的断面功率调整流程</span><span style=\"padding-top: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; border: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.875em; display: block; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.8rem;\">Fig. 4 Flow chart of transient stability constrained section active power flow adjustment</span></sapn></p><p state=\"2\" alt=\"图5\" id=\"outline_anchor_15\" style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\"><sapn style=\"width: 150px; clear: right; float: right; margin-top: 1.2rem; margin-left: 1rem; padding-top: 1.2rem; padding-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; border-left: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);\"><a href=\"http://e-press.dwjs.com.cn/pcsee/periodical/html/2018-38-09-2531/img_7.png\" title=\"图5  \r\n            IEEE 39节点系统\r\n           <span>Fig. 5  \r\n            IEEE 39-bus system\r\n          </span>\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\"><img src=\"http://e-press.dwjs.com.cn/pcsee/periodical/html/2018-38-09-2531/img_7.png\" style=\"width: 130px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 1px; display: block;\"></a><span style=\"padding-top: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; border: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.875em; display: block; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.8rem;\">图5 IEEE 39节点系统</span><span style=\"padding-top: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; border: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.875em; display: block; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.8rem;\">Fig. 5 IEEE 39-bus system</span></sapn></p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">基态潮流方式下,区域C和区域B通过断面<italic>L</italic><sub>1</sub>、<italic>L</italic><sub>2</sub>向区域A输送功率,其中联络线16—17(<italic>l</italic><sub>16-17</sub>)和联络线16—15(<italic>l</italic><sub>16-15</sub>)构成断面<italic>L</italic><sub>1</sub>,联络线25-2(<italic>l</italic><sub>25-2</sub>)和26-27(<italic>l</italic><sub>26-27</sub>)构成断面<italic>L</italic><sub>2</sub>,断面及其联络线的输送功率如<xref ref-type=\"table\" rid=\"T1--0-0-0-1805101434-1\">表1所示。发电机的有功出力上下限及断面<italic>L</italic><sub>1</sub>功率对机组的灵敏度见附录A。</xref></p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">取断面<italic>L</italic><sub>1</sub>为研究断面,通过改变区域A、B内</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\"><sapn style=\"width: 150px; clear: right; float: right; margin-top: 1.2rem; margin-left: 1rem; padding-top: 1.2rem; padding-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; border-left: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);\"><a href=\"http://e-press.dwjs.com.cn/pcsee/periodical/html/2018-38-09-2531/img_8.png\" title=\"表1  \r\n          断面及联络线功率\r\n         <span>Tab. 1  \r\n          Power flow of interface and its transmission lines\r\n        </span>\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\"><img src=\"http://e-press.dwjs.com.cn/pcsee/periodical/html/2018-38-09-2531/img_8.png\" style=\"width: 130px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 1px; display: block;\"></a><span style=\"padding-top: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; border: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.875em; display: block; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.8rem;\">表1 断面及联络线功率</span><span style=\"padding-top: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; border: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.875em; display: block; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.8rem;\">Tab. 1 Power flow of interface and its transmission lines</span></sapn></p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">的发电机有功出力调整断面<italic>L</italic><sub>1</sub>的输送功率,区域C内的发电机不作调整。</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">关联故障：联络线<italic>l</italic><sub>16-17</sub>靠近母线bus-16附近0s发生三相短路,故障持续50ms线路两侧开关三相跳开。基态潮流方式下,系统的暂态稳定裕度<italic>η</italic><sub>0</sub>为0.026742。</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">1）保持暂态稳定裕度不降低,提高断面功率。</p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\">基态潮流方式下,采用数值仿真方法求得暂态稳定裕度对区域A、B内的机组有功出力的灵敏度如<xref ref-type=\"fig\" rid=\"F6--0-0-0-1805101434-1\">图6所示,其中G31号机组为平衡机。</xref></p><p state=\"2\" alt=\"图6\" id=\"outline_anchor_16\" style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 3rem;\"><sapn style=\"width: 150px; clear: right; float: right; margin-top: 1.2rem; margin-left: 1rem; padding-top: 1.2rem; padding-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; border-left: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);\"><a href=\"http://e-press.dwjs.com.cn/pcsee/periodical/html/2018-38-09-2531/img_9.png\" title=\"图6  \r\n            基态潮流方式下的暂态稳定裕度灵敏度\r\n           <span>Fig. 6  \r\n            Transient stability margin sensitivity under initial power flow\r\n          </span>\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\"><img src=\"http://e-press.dwjs.com.cn/pcsee/periodical/html/2018-38-09-2531/img_9.png\" style=\"width: 130px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 1px; display: block;\"></a><span style=\"padding-top: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; border: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.875em; display: block; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.8rem;\">图6 基态潮流方式下的暂态稳定裕度灵敏度</span><span style=\"padding-top: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; border: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.875em; display: block; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.8rem;\">Fig. 6 Transient stability margin sensitivity under initial power flow</span></sapn></p><p style=\"padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: none; font-famil